text: Tovmasyan () is an Armenian surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Lusine Tovmasyan (born 1986), Armenian beauty pageant contestant *Ruben Tovmasyan (1937–2019), Armenian politician *Vache Tovmasyan (born 1986), Armenian actor, comedian and showman *Valentin Tovmasyan (1937-2017), Armenian musicologist Category:Armenian-language surnames
title: Tovmasyan
